u,M}^{k,\ell}$, $1\leq \ell <2M$, defined by $$ G_{
u,M}^{k,\ell}(f)=\left(\int_0^\infty\left|t^{\ell /2+k}\partial _t^kD^{(\ell)}(I-t\Delta _
u)^{-M}(f) ight|^2 rac{dt}{t}ight)^{ rac{1}{2}}, $$ for certain differentiation operator $D^{(\ell)}$.
